alacritty9 — Alacritty 0.17.0 for 9front. Changelog.
(`pac9 changelog alacritty9` shows this; newest first.)

0.2.0 — 2026-07-17
  First versioned release. Rebuilt against a correctness pass on the cc9 C
  runtime the terminal is built on — stubs that used to report success while
  doing nothing (durable fsync, honest file locks, correct O_APPEND, per-thread
  errno, corrected float formatting). No change to the terminal itself: same
  upstream Alacritty 0.17.0, same GL9F frames to the gl9win2 window host,
  render re-verified on bare metal. This just puts alacritty9 on the same
  honest substrate as the rest of the ports. Earlier unversioned installs read
  as '-'; `pac9 upgrade alacritty9` moves them here.
